{"tid":779022,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[食鬼食評]—高質牛肉撈麵","createTime":"2018-08-14T06:35:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T06:18:33.000Z","uid":182683,"like":15,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6bbfafa2b963b16d3909096e0907517826d3a5ad","tid":779022,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:35:52.000Z","msg":"地點：大坑 nagi ramen<br />\n<br />\n今日自製8號波放假，扮下野入大坑食野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好耐冇食依間極隱世小店拉麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有食開拉麵嘅都應該聽過依間野(同豚王打過官司)，平時成日要等位。<br />\n我基本上黎親都會食其間限定，佢地一般個啲豬骨湯底啲普通得濟周街都係就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 ⠀⠀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/142859_d318e7d340f2f7a352909568d4060e0b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F142859_d318e7d340f2f7a352909568d4060e0b.png&h=4052982e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其間限定 安格斯牛肉撈麵$128 ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n味道：<br />\n因為係撈麵嘅關系，我自己覺得麵質應該再硬身同彈牙啲，合格！ <br />\n撈麵好難唔掛汁，所以冇平時有啲拉麵掛唔到湯嘅問題。<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n到個汁啦，超重牛味唔係講笑，勁杰比豪油稀少少，實際我唔知佢點煮，但好大機會係用湯滾到啲水蒸發變左曬勁濃縮(濃湯寶原理)，再加脂肪入去，總之超濃味同偏甜，加埋啲蒜同蔥同埋隻蛋黃，真係食到我停唔到！玩曬啦。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n牛肉亦都好正，都幾多片下，不過瘦左少少，同埋我自己會想表面煎一煎，但可能佢想盡量唔破壞入面啲咁淋嘅肉質所以冇煎到，不過最重要係啲牛肉煮到rare而唔係medium rare，仲食到個種牛肉嘅鮮甜味！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n價錢：<br />\n依碗野份量正常同埋個汁比較肥，絕對夠飽，出面食碗普通拉麵都$100起跳，有啲仲要唔飽，但又唔可以話佢抵食，正常價啦。<br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n評分：8/10<br />\n評語：遲啲食唔番點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost&d=ZKH8qiq0938nELvGat%2FllIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=0b76dd84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b57df5bbde708da2749258602b6ba019e789946","tid":779022,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:40:32.000Z","msg":"天后？"},{"pid":"03aceabf0c552cd430754d150255b64681617aba","tid":779022,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b57df5bbde708da2749258602b6ba019e789946","tid":779022,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:40:32.000Z","msg":"天后？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T07:19:23.000Z","msg":"行入少少"},{"pid":"952d3e5f5157048791f6b894dbd7403eaffd30b3","tid":779022,"uid":134964,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T07:22:44.000Z","msg":"施主，我留意咗你好耐，極度懷疑你係住寶馬山或者大坑home office甚至唔使做嘅小富豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa19d022c92ad4bdbc63b4fb99a88c37c201623","tid":779022,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03aceabf0c552cd430754d150255b64681617aba","tid":779022,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b57df5bbde708da2749258602b6ba019e789946","tid":779022,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T06:40:32.000Z","msg":"天后？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T07:19:23.000Z","msg":"行入少少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T07:34:01.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣同天后中間先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4dae7143787090ae304fafd9134108305fb17a8","tid":779022,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"952d3e5f5157048791f6b894dbd7403eaffd30b3","tid":779022,"uid":134964,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T07:22:44.000Z","msg":"施主，我留意咗你好耐，極度懷疑你係住寶馬山或者大坑home office甚至唔使做嘅小富豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.